module SylvesterKamenikFixtures

# Second-order Sylvester fixtures A·X + B·X·(C ⊗ C) = D captured from
# DifferentiablePerturbation.jl at the canonical pseudo-truth parameter
# point for each of RBC (5×2), RBC_SV (8×4), and SGU (15×7). Each fixture
# returns a NamedTuple (; A, B, C, D, X_ref) where X_ref is the dense
# Kronecker direct-solve ground truth, cross-checked against the Dynare
# GeneralizedSylvesterSolver.jl solution at the time of capture (relative
# discrepancy ≤ 1e-15).
#
# Used by test/test_enzyme_sylvester_kamenik.jl and
# benchmark/sylvester_kamenik.jl.

